---
// index.astro - Keymelo Systems Portfolio Top Page
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Keymelo Systems | Keiji Hirano</title>
  <meta name="description" content="フリーランスITエンジニア Keiji Hiranoのポートフォリオサイト。COBOLから最新技術まで、生命保険システムの深い知見を持つエンジニアです。" />
  <link rel="icon" href="/icon.ico" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Libre+Caslon+Text:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@300;400&family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@300;400;500&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />

  <style>
    :root {
      --bg-primary: #080c10;
      --bg-secondary: #0d1117;
      --bg-card: #111820;
      --accent-primary: #00d4ff;
      --accent-secondary: #0057ff;
      --accent-glow: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.15);
      --text-primary: #e8edf2;
      --text-secondary: #b5cade;
      --text-muted: #3d4f5e;
      --border: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.12);
      --font-display: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      --font-caslon: 'Libre Caslon Text', serif;
      --font-elegant: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      --font-body: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
      --font-mono: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    }

    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      background-color: var(--bg-primary);
      color: var(--text-primary);
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      font-weight: 300;
      line-height: 1.7;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    body::before {
      content: '';
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(rgba(0,212,255,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,212,255,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 60px 60px;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    /* ===== Nav ===== */
    nav {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      z-index: 100;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 1.25rem 4rem;
      background: rgba(8, 12, 16, 0.85);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .nav-logo {
      font-family: var(--font-elegant);
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 2.5rem; list-style: none; }

    .nav-links a {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      text-decoration: none;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }

    .nav-links a::before {
      content: '// ';
      color: var(--accent-primary);
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity 0.2s;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--text-primary); }
    .nav-links a:hover::before { opacity: 1; }

    /* ===== Hero ===== */
    #hero {
      position: relative;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 0 4rem;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .hero-glow {
      position: absolute;
      top: 20%; right: 10%;
      width: 500px; height: 500px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0,87,255,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .hero-glow-2 {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 20%; left: 5%;
      width: 350px; height: 350px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0,212,255,0.07) 0%, transparent 70%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .hero-inner {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 2rem;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 1200px;
      animation: fadeUp 0.9s ease both;
    }

    .hero-brand {
      font-family: var(--font-caslon);
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem);
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--accent-primary);
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      display: block;
    }

    .hero-name {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 7.5vw, 6rem);
      font-weight: 500;
      line-height: 1.05;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
    }

    .hero-desc {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      max-width: 580px;
      line-height: 1.9;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    .hero-cta { display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }

    .hero-logo-area {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: flex-end;
      align-items: center;
      padding-right: 0rem;
      margin-right: -14rem;
    }

    .hero-logo-area img {
      max-width: 100%;
      max-height: 420px;
      object-fit: contain;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 0 40px rgba(0,212,255,0.18));
    }

    .btn-primary {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      padding: 0.85rem 2rem;
      background: var(--accent-primary);
      color: var(--bg-primary);
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.2s;
      clip-path: polygon(0 0, calc(100% - 10px) 0, 100% 10px, 100% 100%, 0 100%);
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      background: #33deff;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,212,255,0.3);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      padding: 0.85rem 2rem;
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-decoration: none;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      transition: all 0.2s;
      clip-path: polygon(0 0, calc(100% - 10px) 0, 100% 10px, 100% 100%, 0 100%);
    }

    .btn-secondary:hover {
      border-color: var(--accent-primary);
      color: var(--accent-primary);
      background: var(--accent-glow);
    }

    /* ===== Section Base ===== */
    section {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      padding: 7rem 4rem;
    }

    .section-header { margin-bottom: 3.5rem; }

    .section-label {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      color: var(--accent-primary);
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.75rem;
    }

    .section-label::before {
      content: '';
      display: block;
      width: 30px; height: 1px;
      background: var(--accent-primary);
    }

    .section-title {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    /* ===== About ===== */
    #about {
      background: var(--bg-secondary);
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .about-content { max-width: 840px; }

    .about-text p {
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.9;
    }

    /* ===== Skills ===== */
    .skills-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .skill-card {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 2rem;
      transition: all 0.3s;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .skill-card::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-glow) 0%, transparent 60%);
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity 0.3s;
    }

    .skill-card:hover { border-color: rgba(0,212,255,0.3); transform: translateY(-4px); }
    .skill-card:hover::after { opacity: 1; }

    .skill-icon {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      color: var(--accent-primary);
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .skill-name {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .skill-desc {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .skill-tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem; margin-top: 1.25rem; }

    .tag {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      color: var(--accent-primary);
      background: rgba(0,212,255,0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,212,255,0.2);
      padding: 0.25rem 0.65rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }

    /* ===== Works ===== */
    #works {
      background: var(--bg-secondary);
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .works-sub-title {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      margin-top: 3.5rem;
      padding-bottom: 0.75rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .works-sub-title:first-of-type { margin-top: 0; }

    .works-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .work-card {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 2.25rem;
      transition: all 0.3s;
    }

    .work-card:hover {
      border-color: rgba(0,212,255,0.3);
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
    }

    /* 制作物カード：GitHubリンク付き */
    .work-card-product {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 2.25rem;
      transition: all 0.3s;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .work-card-product:hover {
      border-color: rgba(0,212,255,0.3);
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
    }

    .work-card-product .work-desc { flex: 1; }

    /* GitHubリンクボタン */
    .work-github-link {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--accent-primary);
      text-decoration: none;
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,212,255,0.25);
      padding: 0.45rem 1rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      transition: all 0.2s;
      width: fit-content;
      clip-path: polygon(0 0, calc(100% - 8px) 0, 100% 8px, 100% 100%, 0 100%);
    }

    .work-github-link:hover {
      background: var(--accent-glow);
      border-color: var(--accent-primary);
    }

    .work-number {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .work-title {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }

    .work-desc {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }

    .work-card-soon {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 1px dashed var(--text-muted);
      padding: 2.25rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 160px;
      opacity: 0.55;
    }

    .work-soon-label {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .work-soon-text {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    /* ===== Contact ===== */
    #contact { text-align: left; }
    .contact-inner { max-width: 560px; }

    .contact-desc {
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      margin: 1.5rem 0 2.5rem;
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.9;
    }

    .contact-links { display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }

    /* ===== Footer ===== */
    footer {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 2rem 4rem;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .footer-logo {
      font-family: var(--font-elegant);
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    }

    .footer-copy {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    }

    /* ===== Animations ===== */
    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
      to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    .fade-up {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
      transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease;
    }

    .fade-up.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

    /* ===== Responsive ===== */
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      nav { padding: 1rem 1.5rem; }
      .nav-links { display: none; }
      section { padding: 5rem 1.5rem; }
      #hero { padding: 0 1.5rem; }
      .hero-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .hero-logo-area { display: none; }
      .skills-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .works-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      footer { padding: 1.5rem; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; text-align: center; }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <nav>
    <a href="#hero" class="nav-logo">Keymelo Systems</a>
    <ul class="nav-links">
      <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
      <li><a href="#skills">Skills</a></li>
      <li><a href="#works">Works</a></li>
      <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>

  <section id="hero">
    <div class="hero-glow"></div>
    <div class="hero-glow-2"></div>
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <span class="hero-brand">Keymelo Systems</span>
        <h1 class="hero-name">Keiji Hirano</h1>
        <p class="hero-desc">ここはフリーランスITエンジニア Keiji Hirano のポートフォリオサイトです。</p>
        <div class="hero-cta">
          <a href="#works" class="btn-primary">実績を見る →</a>
          <a href="#contact" class="btn-secondary">お問い合わせ</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-logo-area">
        <img src="/logo.png" alt="Keymelo Systems Logo" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="about">
    <div class="about-content fade-up">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-label">About</div>
        <h2 class="section-title">Profile</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="about-text">
        <p>大手生命保険のITグループ会社にて、主任・チームリーダーとして個人保険契約管理システムの開発に約8年間従事。要件定義から本番移行まで、プロジェクト全工程を経験してきました。</p>
        <p>COBOLによる生命保険コアシステムの深い業務知識を強みとしながら、Python・Javaによるモダン開発にも積極的に取り組んでいます。</p>
        <p>フリーランスとして、COBOL案件・モダナイゼーション案件を中心に、お客様のシステム課題解決に貢献します。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="skills">
    <div class="section-header fade-up">
      <div class="section-label">Skills</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Skills & Technologies</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="skills-grid">
      <div class="skill-card fade-up">
        <div class="skill-icon">[ 01 ] CORE EXPERTISE</div>
        <div class="skill-name">COBOL / 生命保険システム</div>
        <div class="skill-desc">個人保険契約管理・バッチ処理・帳票設計など、生命保険コアシステムの業務知識と実装経験を深く保有。</div>
        <div class="skill-tags">
          <span class="tag">COBOL</span><span class="tag">生命保険</span><span class="tag">帳票</span><span class="tag">オンライン処理</span><span class="tag">バッチ処理</span><span class="tag">DB2</span><span class="tag">JCL</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-card fade-up">
        <div class="skill-icon">[ 02 ] LANGUAGE</div>
        <div class="skill-name">Python</div>
        <div class="skill-desc">COBOL資産のPython移行実装など、レガシーシステムのモダナイゼーションを実践的に推進中。</div>
        <div class="skill-tags">
          <span class="tag">Python</span><span class="tag">帳票処理</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-card fade-up">
        <div class="skill-icon">[ 03 ] LANGUAGE</div>
        <div class="skill-name">Java</div>
        <div class="skill-desc">業務システム開発における標準言語として習得中。オブジェクト指向設計の知識をCOBOL経験と組み合わせて活用。</div>
        <div class="skill-tags">
          <span class="tag">Java</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-card fade-up">
        <div class="skill-icon">[ 04 ] LANGUAGE</div>
        <div class="skill-name">Kotlin / Android</div>
        <div class="skill-desc">Kotlinを用いたAndroidアプリを自作開発中。モバイルアプリ開発の実践的なスキルを習得中。</div>
        <div class="skill-tags">
          <span class="tag">Kotlin</span><span class="tag">Android</span><span class="tag">アプリ開発</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-card fade-up">
        <div class="skill-icon">[ 05 ] PROJECT LEAD</div>
        <div class="skill-name">設計 / PL / チームリード</div>
        <div class="skill-desc">要件定義〜本番移行まで全工程を経験。最大10名チームのPLとして複数プロジェクトを完遂。OJT担当経験もあり。</div>
        <div class="skill-tags">
          <span class="tag">要件定義</span><span class="tag">基本設計</span><span class="tag">PL</span><span class="tag">OJT</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-card fade-up">
        <div class="skill-icon">[ 06 ] QUALIFICATIONS</div>
        <div class="skill-name">情報処理資格</div>
        <div class="skill-desc">高度情報処理技術者（システムアーキテクト）取得。設計・アーキテクチャの深い知識を保有。</div>
        <div class="skill-tags">
          <span class="tag">システムアーキテクト</span><span class="tag">応用情報</span><span class="tag">基本情報</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="works">
    <div class="section-header fade-up">
      <div class="section-label">Works</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">実績・制作物</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="works-sub-title fade-up">主要プロジェクト実績</div>
    <div class="works-grid">
      <div class="work-card fade-up">
        <div class="work-number">PROJECT_01 / PL担当 / 10名 × 9ヶ月</div>
        <div class="work-title">保険料収納代行システム移行</div>
        <div class="work-desc">みずほ銀行収納代行サービス停止に伴う大規模移行プロジェクト。コンビニ経由の保険料収納システムを新システム（三井住友銀行のシステムに対応）へ移行し、HULFT経由でのデータ受信および社内システムにおけるデータ処理に対応。PLとして全体を統括。</div>
        <div class="skill-tags"><span class="tag">COBOL</span><span class="tag">PL</span><span class="tag">大規模移行</span><span class="tag">HULFT</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="work-card fade-up">
        <div class="work-number">PROJECT_02 / PL担当 / 6名 × 6ヶ月</div>
        <div class="work-title">名義変更システム タブレット端末対応</div>
        <div class="work-desc">保険契約の名義変更（受取人変更）システムをタブレット端末で稼働させる対応。ホスト稼働部分の要件定義から本番移行までを担当。</div>
        <div class="skill-tags"><span class="tag">COBOL</span><span class="tag">PL</span><span class="tag">タブレット連携</span></div>
